  <title>Description</title>
  <titlealts>
    <searchtitle>Data Element: ORGANISATION SITE IDENTIFIER (OF PROVIDER CANCER DECISION TO TREAT) - Description</searchtitle>
  </titlealts>
  <body>
  <div>
      <p>
         <xref outputclass="element"
               keyref="element_organisation_site_identifier__of_provider_cancer_decision_to_treat_">ORGANISATION SITE IDENTIFIER (OF PROVIDER CANCER DECISION TO TREAT)</xref>
 is the same as attribute 
              <xref outputclass="attribute" keyref="attribute_organisation_site_identifier">ORGANISATION SITE IDENTIFIER</xref>.        </p>
      <p>
         <xref outputclass="element"
               keyref="element_organisation_site_identifier__of_provider_cancer_decision_to_treat_">ORGANISATION SITE IDENTIFIER (OF PROVIDER CANCER DECISION TO TREAT)</xref>
 is the 
              <xref outputclass="attribute" keyref="attribute_organisation_site_identifier">ORGANISATION SITE IDENTIFIER</xref>
 of the 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_organisation_site">ORGANISATION SITE</xref>
 acting as 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_health_care_provider">Health Care Provider</xref>
 where the decision to treat the 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENT</xref>
 was made which initiated a 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_cancer_care_plan">Cancer Care Plan</xref>
 with one or more 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_planned_cancer_treatment">Planned Cancer Treatments</xref>.        </p>
      <p>
The 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_planned_cancer_treatment">Planned Cancer Treatment</xref>
 may be planned and provided by a different 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_health_care_provider">Health Care Provider</xref>.        </p>
  </div>
